\id 2CO Tutsa: Bible Translation 1st Edition 
\h 2 Korinte 
\toc1 KORINTE suh Pool ih Taklih raang arah Le 
\toc2 2 Korinte 
\toc3 2Kr 
\mt1 KORINTE 
\mt2 Suh Pool ih Taklih Raang Arah Le 
\imt1 Ephangjatjih 
\ip Pool ih taknyi le raangta ah langla Korin chaaste chikrokta doh sano thiinmui suh raangmaatta. Mararah chaaste loong ah Pool damdi rapne ih thichomuita, enoothong erah jat ano Pool neng damdi sano thiinmui suh neng suh jatthuk thunta. 
\ip Le phangraang ano Pool ih Korin chaaste damdi sano pak tiit jangbaat rumha, heh ih baat rumha Korin chaaste ih ethih choh rum abah uh nyia heh jengdaan rum abah uh neng ih sekthun rumha nyia seklilih ih roongwaan rumla asuh Pool rapne ih roonla. Erah lih adi Judia dowa Kristaan loong asuh lomse rum ano chosok raangmaat rumha. Leedaap thoon raangha adi Pool ih heh kaamwah tiit ah baat ha, tiimnge liidi Korin ni mararah mina ih Pool suh lalangka kaamwah ngeh ih li rumta eno neng teewah suh ah ami eh liirumta. 
\iot Hemong Dowa Jatjih 
\io1 Ephangjatjih \ior (1:1-11)\ior* 
\io1 Pool nyia Korin chaas \ior (1:12—7:16)\ior* 
\io1 Judia dowa Kristaan loong raangtaan ih ngun lomse theng \ior (8:1—9:15)\ior* 
\io1 Pool ih heh teewah kaamwah nyia chaan aphaan tiit ah baat ha\ior (10:1—13:10)\ior* 
\io1 Jengthoon \ior (13:11-13)\ior* 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Esm 18:1\x* Rangte thung jun ih Jisu Kristo kaamwah Pool nyia seng phono Timothi taangnawa- 
\p Arah langla Korin dowa Rangte chaaste nyia Akaia hadaang dowa Rangte mina loong raangtaan: 
\p  
\v 2 Seng loong Wah Rangte nyia Teesu Jisu Kristo minchan sen damdoh toom tongha adoleh semroongroong ih toomtong an. 
\s1 Rangte suh Pool ih lakookmi liita 
\p  
\v 3 Seng Wah Rangte nyia Teesu Jisu Kristo Wah suh lakookmi li ih, seng minchante Wah, heh juuba jirep adi seng moot chosokte Rangte!  
\v 4 Seng chamnaang di heh ih chosok hali, erah thoidi seng chamnaang li likhiik o mina chamnaangla erah jen chosok hi, erah langla Rangte taangnawa chohi ah likhiik ih chosok hi.  
\v 5 Seng loong ah Kristo mendi rapne ih chamnaangli ah likhiik ih, Rangte taangnawa mootchoh ah uh emamah ih chohi.  
\v 6 Seng loong chamnaang ebah, erah sen khopi raangtaan nyia sen moot chosok suh; seng loong ah chosok he bah, sen uh chosok ih han eno seng ih naanhi ajih sen ih uh cham anaang ah ejen naan ih an.  
\v 7 Erah raangtaan ih sen suh lasoot lasaam ih laalomli; seng ih jat ehi sen loong ah seng damdi roong chamnaang halan, erah likhiik sen ih uh seng chosok hali ah likhiik eroong choh ehan. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt 1Kr 15:32\x* Joonte loong, Esia hani chamchoti ah sen loong asuh jatthuk suh liihi. Seng erah than ih siiwii chamnaangti thingtong esuh ju takah jook laalomti.  
\v 9 Seng loong ah tek haat suh mat jen paat ih rumta ngeh ih samthunti. Enoothong erah angta ah langla seng teenuh teewah suh latuumaang thang ih Rangte suh tuumaang theng o ih etek nawa ngaakthing thukla asuh ah.  
\v 10 Etek ejih choophaanphaan angta dowa heh ih puipang hali, heh ih ju puipang hali; eno sen rangsoom ni chosok hali jun ih seng we puipang ehe,  
\v 11 sen rangsoom nawa ih seng chosok tahe ah likhiik ah. Erah thoidi mina hantek ih seng suh rangsoom kohali ah echaat eh ah, eno Rangte ih romseetam kot ih he; eno seng loong raangtaan ih mina hantek tui nah heh suh lakookmi liirum ah. 
\s1 Pool mongtham ah elek eta 
\p  
\v 12 Seng loong khuupookli ah langla, arah mongrep adi sen damdi joonte sano angli roidong ah phanjangjang, eno erah seklilih\f + \fr 1:12 \ft seklilih\ft mararah le ni \fq esa liiha.\f* nyia ladem laju angli ah Rangte lakkot, erah jun ih pan hali adoleh erah mina mongtham nawa tah angka Rangte minchan nyia chaan aphaan nawa.  
\v 13 Seng ih raangkohi le ah an sen ih mi wet ehan nyia jat ehan. Enoothong amadi sen ih tanang jatwe ri,  
\v 14 liwang nah naririh ih jat he ngeh ih tuumaangli, tiimnge liidi sen suh khuupookli ah likhiik Teesu Jisu raaha doh sen uh seng raangtaan ih khuupook etheng toom ang ah. 
\p  
\v 15 Erah loong asuh ngah rapne ih tuumaang angno sen reeni jaakhoh dongkhoom suh taatchung tang, sen loong ah ih romseetam ah dopnyi toomchoh an suh ah.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 1:16 \xt Esm 19:21\x* Ngah Mesidonia nah kah angdoh sen reenah dongkhoom chungtang, eno Mesidonia nawa we ngaak wang hang adoh Judia nah toom diisiit kaat he suh ah.  
\v 17 Erah chungtang ah doondaak chung tam etang? Adoleh erah hansi tenthun nawa ih tamchung tang, pootsiit doh “thangroh, thangroh” nyia “daanroh, daanroh” esuh ah.  
\v 18 Rangte ami tiit jeng jengla likhiik, “thangroh thangroh” ih angno “daanroh daanroh” esuh ngah ih kah takham tang.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Esm 18:5\x* Rangte Sah, Jisu Kristo, marah Silas nyia Timothi sengjom ih baatti abah, “danroh” esuh nyia “thangroh” esuh tah angka. Erah tokkhodi Rangte raangtaan ih heh ih thangroh ete;  
\v 20 tiimnge liidi Rangte kakhamte asuh heh ih “Em” liite. Erah raangtaan ih Jisu Kristo jun ih “Amen” ah Rangte men raksiit suh liihi.  
\v 21 Rangte heh teeteewah seng nyia seng loong ah, eroom ih dongsiit tahe, Kristo damdoh seng roidong ah rongtangtang angsuh ah; Rangte heh teeteewah ih danje tahe,  
\v 22 Rangte heh teeteewah ih seng changte ngeh ih hemen jatthuk suh sin hoon hali, eno seng ten ni Esa Chiiala ah koheeno seng raangtaan ih ban thiinha asuh kamkam ih tuumaang thuk hali. 
\p  
\v 23 Rangte suh nga ih nga haaki ngeh ih poonhang —heh ih nga tenthun ah ejat ih halang! Ngah Korin ni lakaat aju sen loong phocham an ngeh ih tara tahang.  
\v 24 Sen suh hanpi jaatjaat etheng ngeh ih talaat baatke; seng ih jat ehi sen loong hanpi ah rongtangtang ngeh ah, seng damdi roong mokah hali abah sen tenroon raangtaan ih boh mokah hali. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Erah raangtaan ih sen loong reenah we dongkhoom hangno sen loong thungthet thuk suh tanooktang.  
\v 2 Tiimnge liidi sen loong ah we thungthet thuk rumha bah nga tenroon thukte ah o ah we ang ah?  
\v 3 Erah thoidi nga ih le raangmaat tahang—tiimnge liidi ngah kaat kangno nga tenroon thukte loong ah phothungthih ah ngeh ah. Ngah ih jat ih rumhala, ngah tenroon angdi sen uh tenroon anglan ngeh ah.  
\v 4 Sen loong asuh nga mikse ah janhaat angno hu ang ih le raangmaat tahang; erah langla sen thungthet thuksuh tah angka, sen loong ih nga minchan ah toomjat rum ah ngeh ih raangmaat tahang. 
\s1 Thetreete raang ih biin anaan 
\p  
\v 5 Amadi, o bah uh mararah ih thungthet eh thukla, erah ngah tathungthet thuk rang sen thungthet thuk halan—thidokdok lah angka bah uh ah. (Arah jenglang ah langla heh raangtaan ih ngah naktoom thih ang.)  
\v 6 Sen dung dowa ehanko ah ih wasiit mipuh ah erah than chamthuk lan ah echang e ah.  
\v 7 Erabah uh, amadoh, sen ih heh thidokdok ih phothungthih asuh biin anaan hoon anno chaankot jengkhaap ah jeng koh an.  
\v 8 Eno amiisak di sen ih heh minchan han tiit ah heh su jat ih thuk an ngeh ih sen lasih jorum hala.  
\v 9 Erah raangtang abah sen loong ah ih phate joonnaam ah tamjen naan rumha eno jirep adi nga jeng chaatchaat tam ih rumla ngeh ih raangtang.  
\v 10 Mina loong mokre ah biin anaan hoon andi, ngah ih uh biin anaan ehang. Marah biin anaan hoonjih ah—erah biin anaan hoon ang adi—Jisu Kristo ngathong ni sen raangtaan ih hoon hang,  
\v 11 erah seng sak nah Soitaan ah naktoom mi mokah ah ngeh ih reelang; tiimnge liidi seng ih heh mongtham kaankoong ah jat ehi. 
\s1 Troas ni Pool tenchi angta 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Esm 2:1\x* Kristo Ruurang Ese tiit ah baat suh Troas ni thok tahang adoh, erah nah heh mootkaat raang ih seng Teesu ih lam laangkoh ah jat etang.  
\v 13 Enoothong seng phono Taitaas ah lajaptup keeno, Ngah rapne ih sootsaam tang. Erah raangtaan ih miloong ah damdi raajeng angno Mesidonia ni katang. 
\s1 Kristo mendoh jen ih 
\p  
\v 14 Enoothong Rangte suh seng ih jengseera ih! Tiimnge liidi Kristo damdi roop eno ejen lam ni Rangte ih siit hali. Rangte ih seng loong ah Kristo tiit noongrep ni tumbaat suh phontum likhiik ih maak hali.  
\v 15 Erah langla seng loong ah Kristo ih Rangte suh phontumkaang tummangmang eh tingtakkoh ah likhiik, erah mirep miraang reeni thoktum kala, mattekte angkoja adoleh khopi chote angkoja.  
\v 16 Eno erah tingtakta ah ematte loong raangtaan ebah neng tek thuk suh nambokbok; enoothong khopui chote loong raangtaan ebah roidong chotheng tummangmang?  
\v 17 Seng loong ah wahoh loong ah likhiik tah angke, neng loong ah ih bah Rangte jengkhaap ah thaangne huikhaak sang arah likhiik mok samthun rumha; enoothong seng loong abah Rangte ih kaat thuk thoidi heh ngathong ni Kristo laksuh ngeh ih jengkongli. 
\c 3  
\s1 Jengdang ena laksuh loong 
\p  
\v 1 Erah jengli ah seng khuurong pook tiit we baat ih arah likhiik tam ah? Mina wahoh loong ah likhiik, seng raang ih sen suh le phanraangkot tam jamhi adoleh sen jiin nawa phanraangkot ah jamhi?  
\v 2 Seng maangka di bah sen teeteewah ah ju seng leeraang, mirep miraang ih jattheng ah seng ten ni raangthiin hi.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Hpkt 24:12; \xt Jer 31:33; Ijk 11:19; 36:26\x* Erah jatririh, arah le ah Kristo heh teeteewah ih raangta eno erah le ah seng ih sen suh maatti. Erah roong ih raang arah tah angta, ething Rangte Chiiala nawa ih raangta, adoleh jongkhoh ni taraangta mina ten ni raangta. 
\p  
\v 4 Seng arah jengli ah Kristo jun ih Rangte suh kamkam ih tuumaang eno jengli.  
\v 5 Arah mootkaat ah seng ih jen ih ngeh ih jen chaangjih seng suh tiim uh tajeeka. Seng jen mookaat jih abah Rangte jiin nawa raahala;  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Jer 31:31\x* jengdang ena jun ih jen mokali abah Rangte thoidi bo ah, erah lakraang hootthe tah angka erabah Chiiala ni. Lakraang hootthe ih bah etek ba chothuk ho, enoothong Chiiala ih bah roidong koho. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Hpkt 34:29\x* Hootthe ah jongkho ni raang kota, eno erah kota adoh Rangte chaan aphaan ah dongjat thuk rumta. Moses the akhoh phaak ah taat moondat adi uh Ijirel mina loong ah ih neng mik ih tanaan sok rumta. Enoobah Hootthe marah ih etek ih thukla ah emathan ih phaakjaaja ang abah,  
\v 8 Chiiala nawa ih mokala ah tiimthan ephaak ang ah.  
\v 9 Dut haat etheng banlam ah erah than ih ephaak ang abah; khopiiroidong kotjih banlam ah tang tiimthan ephaak ang ah!  
\v 10 Seng ih jen li eh ih amadi phaakla ah ehan ephaak ang kano maangdi phaakjaaja angta ah emat eh kala.  
\v 11 Eno pootsiit phaakta rah botseh erah than ih phaakta, saarookwet phaakla ah tang tiimthan ephaak ang ah! 
\p  
\v 12 Erah thoidi erah suh laalom ih no, seng loong ah rongtangtang angli.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Hpkt 34:33\x* Seng Moses likhiik tah angke, Moses ih bah hethe hekhoh ah moondat kano Ijirel mina loong ih phojat johang ngeh ih hethe hekhoh ah loop eta.  
\v 14 Nengthung nengtak ah, erah di maalah, muuhoom rumta; amadi tuk ih nengthung nengtak ah jengdang ehak ah taatweh rum abah uh maangdi loopta the akhoh likhiik ih emamah ih muuhoom rumha. Neng loopta nyuh abah Kristo damdoh roop ano luulu ba khook haat ah.  
\v 15 Amadi uh, Moses Hootthe ah weh rum adi erah loopta rah ih neng thung ah muutu thuk rumla.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Hpkt 34:34\x* Enoothong, Rangteele ni Moses suh liiha ah likhiik: “Hethe hekhoh loop ah Teesu reeni thok kohaano khook haat\f + \fr 3:16 \ft Hewet 16 ah amah jen lek raang ih ah: Enoothong o ang bah uh hetheeloop ah Teesu reeni thok haano dok haat ah.\f* eta.  
\v 17 Amadi, “Teesu” ah Chiiala ni; eno marah di Teesu Chiiala jeela, eradi maama pongwan angla.  
\v 18 Erah thoidi, seng loong the akhoh laloop thang ih Teesu chaan aphaan ah sengthe sengkhoh ni phaak thukli, erah Teesu reenawa, phosiitsiit ih phaakla, eno erah langla Chiiala, eno erah ih seng loong ah saarookwet phaak raangtaan ih heh likhiik ih leksiit hali. 
\c 4  
\s1 Paak tekpoh ni Chiiala 
\p  
\v 1 Rangte ih tenthet heeno arah mootkaat ah mootthuk hali, erah raang ih seng thung tajoongke.  
\v 2 Seng ih husah tiit nyia rakrek tiit ah thiinhaat ehi; seng ih mimok miwaan tah angke adoleh Rangte jengkhaap uh tamoong baatke. Rangte miksokdi seng loong ah amiisak weephaak adi tongli eno seng teeteewah tiit deenbaat hi ah mirep thung nah seng mokali ese ngeh ih toom jatrum ah ngeh ih taat thunhi.  
\v 3 Eno seng ih ruurang ese tiit ah huthiin ih bah, ematte loong raangtaan ih ba ang ah.  
\v 4 Neng loong ah ih tahanpi rumka, tiimnge liidi nengthung nengtak ah arah mongrep dowa hakhoh luuwang lakhui ni rangnak ni thiinha. Neng loong asuh neng khothung ni phaakta we ah tatup thuk rumta, erah weephaak ah langla Kristo rangka suh Ruurang Ese tiit dowa dongta, erah amiisak Rangte likhiik ih angta.  
\v 5 Tiimnge liidi erah seng teewah tiit tabaatti; seng ih bah Jisu Kristo ah Teesu nge ih baatti, eno Jisu thoilam di seng loong sen laksuh eh hoonli.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Rangph 1:3\x* Erah thoidi Rangte ih liita, “Weephaak ah rangnak mong nawa dongphaak ah” erah langla Kristo the akhoh ni Rangte chaan aphaan phaak thukla ah seng suh jatthuk suh weephaak phaak thukte Rangte ah likhiik. 
\p  
\v 7 Enoothong chaan aphaan elongthoon ah Rangte taang ni, seng taang ni tah angka ngeh ih jatthuk suh chiiala ah paaktek ni lomthiin hi ah likhiik.  
\v 8 Ehanko ah seng loong ah echam eli, erabah uh seng tak sengseng abah tathoonka; tiimsaasa di tenchi angli, enoothong thung mabah uh tasaap datke;  
\v 9 piiara hantek je ah, erabah uh seng joonte laje mabah uh tah angke; tiimsaasa di maak uh edan ehi, erabah uh ethet sengseng abah tah eke.  
\v 10 Saarookwet di etek si ang ih bah uh Jisu tiita ah seng ih huiroh ehi, tiimnge liidi heh roidong ah seng roidong nah uh toomtup asuh ah.  
\v 11 Seng roi roitang Jisu thoilam di seng roidong ah choothaat thaat eh hoonla, tiimnge liidoh Jisu roidong ah seng hansi roidong doh mih ih japtup etheng.  
\v 12 Erah langla etek ah seng damdi jeeroh eh hala, enoothong erah thaang ah roidong ah sen damdoh roong mokaha. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Rsb 116:10\x* Rangteele ni liiha, “Ngah ih hanpi eh thoidi jengtang.” Phoosiitsiit moong achaang ah hanpi thoidi seng loongtang ih hanpi hi.  
\v 14 Seng loong ah ih jat ehi, Rangte ih Teesu Jisu ah roidong kotsuh ngaaksaat siitta, seng loong ah uh sen damdoh heh teewah pandoh emamah ih roidong kotsuh heh damdoh ngaak saatsiit he.  
\v 15 Erah loong ah sen thoilam doh ang ah; eno Rangte minchan ah mina ehanhan re nah thok ah, neng loong ah ih Rangte rangka suh neng rangsoom nah ehanhan lakookmi li ah. 
\s1 Tuumaang nah songtong tiit 
\p  
\v 16 Erah raangtaan ih seng thung tajoongke. Seng hansi roidong ah hiitle hiitle ih enaang ekah ah bah uh, chiiala ni seng loong ah rangwu saakaan rookwet ena ih hoonli.  
\v 17 Eno pootsiit chamnaang li rah ih seng loong ah erah nang ih elong ah phaakjaaja ih hoon thuk he.  
\v 18 Tiimnge liidi seng mik ih tup hi adi seng thun takoke, latupke adi seng thung ah kohi. Seng mik ih tup hi abah pootsiit raang ih ba, enoothong mik ih latupke ah langla saarookwet raangtaan ih tongla. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 Seng loong ih jat ehi seng tongli nyutaap ah— arah hah dowa seng sakpuh ah—ethet eh ah, seng songtong theng nok abah Rangte ih rangmong ni ethiin eha, erah nok ah heh teeteewah ih mabah uh lathet theng ih hoonha.  
\v 2 Eno amadi seng tak ah dongheeng hi, rangmong ni seng nok hoonthiin ha ah seng sakkhoh nah baalah loop tahe ngeh ih samthunhi;  
\v 3 eno erah nyuh ah wok ih no nyumuh khatmuh lah angsuh ah.  
\v 4 Seng loong ah arah hah dowa nyutaap adi tong ih adi, seng siiwi chamnaang ni thungjoong tongli, enoothong arah hatoh dowa sakphu ah thiinhaat eh suh tah angka; erah nang ih bah rangmong dowa ah seng sak nah toom loop he ngeh ih thunhi, eno juuba etek jaat ah roidong ih hoon ah.  
\v 5 Rangte heh luulu juuba seng leksiitte warah ah, eno seng raangtaan eh chojih ban khookham thiinha ah chowang suh Chiiala ah kohali. 
\p  
\v 6 Erah raangtaan ih seng loong ah saarookwet lacho laphaan ih tongli. Seng ih jat ehi arah sakpuh adoh mathan ih tong ih eradoh ba seng ah Teesu nok nawa haloh angli.  
\v 7 Tiimnge liidi seng roidong ah seng tuumaang jun ih ang ah, mik ih tupjih tah angka.  
\v 8 Seng loong ah lacho laphaan ih ang eno seng sakpuh roidong ah thiinhaat ih no Teesu jiin nawa nok adoh wang suh liihi.  
\v 9 Tiim nang ih ju elong ah langla, seng ih Rangte tenroon thuk suh liihi, arah nah angkoja oh adoleh erah nawa angkoja oh.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Rom 14:10\x* Tiimnge liidi seng loong ah thoontang heh ih dande suh Kristo ngathong nah dong ejih ang ah. Seng hansi roidong di ethih angkoja oh ese angkoja oh, o mama mokati, erah jun ih echoh eh ih. 
\s1 Kristo jun ih Rangte damdi joonte 
\p  
\v 11 Rangte ra cho theng ah tiimjih suh liiha ah erah seng ih jat ehi, erah raangtaan ih wahoh loong ah roonphak suh taatchung hi. Seng loong ah Rangte ih jirep adi jat hali, eno sen ih ngah uh sen ten nawa ih jat eh hali ngeh ih laalomlang.  
\v 12 Seng ih seng teewah tiit we baat suh taliike; erah nang ih bah, seng thoidi khuupook lan ah tiimjih thoilam di ah erah jatthuk suh taat thunhi, eno juuba o mina neng dangjang nyia neng jaase suh khuupookla loong asuh jen ngaak baattaan an.  
\v 13 Seng loong ah seng thung tam phaangli? Emah ang abah Rangte thoilam di angla. Adoleh seng thung tam sekli? Emah ang abah erah sen raangtaan ih ang ah.  
\v 14 Seng loong ah Kristo minchan ih pan hali, amadi, seng ih jat ehi mirep raangtaan ih wasiit roop tiita, erah langla erah tiila adi warep roongroopla.  
\v 15 Heh loongtang raangtaan ih tiita, tiimnge liidi o ething tongla ah neng teeteewah raang ih tathing tongka enoothong neng raangtaan ih ti ano we ngaaksaatta warah raangtaan ih tongla. 
\p  
\v 16 Erah raangtaan ih, seng ih o uh mina jun ih tadande ke. Seng ih jaasiit Kristo ah mina jun ih mok samthunti bah uh, seng erah likhiik takah reeraang ke.  
\v 17 O mina Kristo raangtaan ih angla heh ena ih hoonla; ehak ah kaat eta, ena thok hala.  
\v 18 Erah loong ah Rangte mokala, seng loong ah piiara dowa heh joonte hoonthuk hali eno erah likhiik wahoh uh joonte hoonthuk suh seng suh baat hali.  
\v 19 Tiitkhaap seng ih baattheng ah langla Rangte ih mina loongtang Kristo jun ih heh joonte ang thukla.\f + \fr 5:19 \fq Rangte ih mina loongtang Kristo jun ih heh joonte ang thukla; \ft adoleh \fq mina loongtang heh joonte hoon thukta di Rangte ah Kristo damdi angta.\f* Neng loong rangdah ah Rangte ih talom thiinka, eno seng loong asuh neng loong ah heh joonte mamah ih hoonta erah tiitkhaap ah baat hali. 
\p  
\v 20 Erah thoidi, Rangte ih seng loong jun ih jatthuk tahan ah likhiik seng loong ah Kristo raangtaan ih jengli. Kristo mendi seng ih sen lasih johi: Rangte ih sen loong ah piiara dowa heh joonte ih toom hoonthuk han!  
\v 21 Kristo ah rangdah tah angta, enoothong seng loong raangtaan ih Rangte ih seng rangdah roong hui thukta tiimnge liidi heh jun ih Rangte jiin dowa kateng ah seng ih nep roong chosuh ah. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Rangte mootkaatte jun ih eroom ih mokali, eno, sen loong asuh Rangte tenthet erah chohi ah thaangmuh nah naktoom ang ah.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Isa 49:8\x* Rangte jengla ah boichaat an: 
\q1 “Sen loong rongthu suh nga saapoot thok taha di, 
\q2 Sen jeng ngah ih boichaat etang, 
\q1 Sen loong puipang rangwu thok taha adi, 
\q2 Sen loong ah chosok ih rum taha.” 
\m Boichaat an! Arah saapoot ah Rangte ih seng rongthu saapoot; chiinnyah sa seng puipang rangwu ah! 
\p  
\v 3 Seng mootkaat pakna ah o ih uh naktoom thetsok ah ngeh ih thunhi, erah raang ih o lam nah uh lamtang nak toom ang ah ngeh ih taat thunhi.  
\v 4 Erah nang ih bah, Rangte laksuh jun ih seng loong ah ih chamchoh di angkoja oh, echeh echaan di angkoja oh nyia chikrok di angkoja oh enaan ehi ah thong noisok hi.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Esm 16:23\x* Seng loong ah ebot ih tahe, phaatak ni sak tahe, nyia midung ni kiipnak tahe; moot akaat uh jupmuh saatmuh adoleh phakmuh satmuh ih kati.  
\v 6 Seng loong ah saachamcham ang eno, mongtham je ano, enaan nyia minchan ah je ano seng loong Rangte laksuh ngeh ih noisok hi —Esa Chiiala nawa ih nyia seng amiisak mongnook nawa ih ah,  
\v 7 amiisak tiit ah baat hi dowa ih, nyia Rangte chaan aphaan nawa ih ah. Seng ih piiara long suh nyia seng teewah puipang suh kateng ah senglang sengpah eh kap hi.  
\v 8 Seng loong ah soomtu nep eh hali nyia rakri thuk nep eh hali; adoleh kaanju uh kaanju eh hali nyia phoongpha uh phoongpha eh hali. Seng loong asuh khoonglap liihe bah uh seng loong ih amiisak tiit ah baat hi;  
\v 9 warep ih jat ehe bah uh lajatri likhiik; seng loong ah tekchoi likhiik, enoothong sen miksok di seng loong ah ething. Seng loong ah siiwi he bah uh tathet haatri;  
\v 10 saarookwet thungthet eh ih bah uh tenroon ih tongli; seng changthih likhiik ang ih bah uh, warep changteng eh hoonthukli; seng jiinni tiim lajeeka likhiik ang ih bah uh, amiisak di seng taang ni jaatrep jeela. 
\p  
\v 11 Korin ni tongte joon awaan loong! Sen loong asuh wuusa ih liihi; sen loong ah seng thung ni thun ehi.  
\v 12 Sen loong raang ih seng thung tamake; sen loong thung ba malan.  
\v 13 Sen loong asuh nga susah suh baatbaat ih rumhala: Erah tenthun ah likhiik ih sen tenthun uh noisok ehe. Sen uh emamah ang an. 
\s1 Rangnak mina likhiik lah angtheng 
\p  
\v 14 Lahanpiite loong reeraangla ah likhiik nak reeraang an, emah tajen reekan. Epun nyia lapunka ah mabah uh phoosiit mamah mi ang ah? Rangwu nyia rangnak ah eroom ih mamah mi ang ah?  
\v 15 Kristo nyia Hakhoh Luuwang ah mamah mi tungchan ah? Hanpiite loong lahanpiite damdi tiim adi phoosiit angla?  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt 1Kr 3:16; 6:19; \xt Lew 26:12; Ijk 37:27\x* Rangte rangsoomnok nyia rangnak mih soom nok ah mamah mi tungchan ah? Tiimnge liidi seng loong ah ething tong Rangte nok! Rangte heh teeteewah ih liita, 
\q1 “Ngah ih nga nok ah nga mina loong damdoh hoon ang 
\q2 neng damdoh roomtong ang; 
\q1 Ngah neng Rangte ang ang, 
\q2 eno neng loong ah nga noksong ang ah.” 
\m  
\v 17 \x - \xo 6:17 \xt Isa 52:11\x* Erah raangtaan ih Teesu ih liiha, 
\q1 “Sen ih neng loong thiinhaat ih an 
\q2 eno sen ih neng loong ah thiinhaat ih an. 
\q1 Esot damdoh sen reejih tiim uh tajeeka, 
\q2 eno juuba ngah ih sen loong ah kap rumha. 
\q1  
\v 18 \x - \xo 6:18 \xt 1Tet 17:13; Isa 43:6; Jer 31:9\x* Ngah sen wah ang ang, 
\q2 eno sen loong ah ngaasuh ngaasah ang an, Teesu Elongthoon ih liiha.” 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1 Joon awaan loong, arah kakham loong thoontang seng raangtaan ih hoonta. Erah raangtaan ih, seng teenuh teewah ih seng sakpuh adoleh chiiala nyaan hoomte dowa esa angjih, Rangte soomtu lam ih seng loong ah esa ih songtong theng. 
\s1 Pool tenroon 
\p  
\v 2 Sen ten nah seng samthun roh ehe. Seng ih o uh tathet thukke; o uh tathet haatke adoleh o thet thuk suh uh tachungke.  
\v 3 Arah jenglang ah sen dut haat suh tali kang; jaakhoh di uh ebaat ih rum taha, seng loong ah ething ang koji oh adoleh tekmang ang koji oh sen loong ah seng minchante saarookwet eroomroom ih angli.  
\v 4 Ngah sen loong asuh kamkam ih tuumaang lang; nyia sen loong sok rum haano rapne ih khuupook lang! Seng chamnaang di uh nga tenchaan ih tonglang; nga rapne tenroon ju tonglang. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt 2Kr 2:13\x* Mesidonia ni thok lidi uh, seng loong ah naangtong muh. Erah ni noongrep ni cham anaang tola angdowa, rookmui jengmui, nyia seng ten ni choothaat thaat totoh angdowa.  
\v 6 Enoothong, thungjoongte suh chaan kotte Rangte, ih Taitaas ah kaat thuk haano sen chaan kok dongta.  
\v 7 Seng loong ah heh kaat suh luulu taroonti, heh suh sen ih mamah ih rongthu tan erah baat heeno ehan roonti. Nga japtup suh sen mamah ramtan erah ah baat ih tahe, nga raangtaan ih sen loong ah erathan ih thetthun han, adoleh nga pang suh erathan ih thunhan; erah raangtaan ih amadi ehan roonlang. 
\p  
\v 8 Ngah ih raangmaat tahang le ah ih sen thungthet thuk han bah uh erah raangtang asuh ngah ih tathet thunkang. Sen thungthet ah tuprum haano thetthun ih angbah uh pootsiit raang ba ang ah.  
\v 9 Enoothong amadi ngah roonlang abah—sen thungthet thuk suh tah angka, sen thungthih tan ah ih senkhoom sensaam lekthuk halan asuh roonlang. Erah thungthet ah Rangte ih jat eta, erah raangtaan ih sen thetjih seng tiim uh re muh.  
\v 10 Tiimnge liidi Rangte ih thungthet marah suh liiha erah ih bah tenthun ah lek thuk ano khopiiroidong lam ah suiha—eno erah di thetthunjih tajeeka! Enoothong mina thungthet luulu ih bah etek ba eh thuk ho.  
\v 11 Erah thungthih tan thoidi Rangte mamah mokala erah taat sok thaak an: Sen thung mathan sekthuk halan, sen toongtang ah jat eh thuk halan! Punkhat ela ngeh ih jatthuk halan, etek nawa pang hali ngeh ih jatthuk halan, seng raangtaan ih thunha ngeh ih jatthuk halan, nyia emoong reete chamthuk suh ban tongroh ela ngeh ih jatthuk halan. Jirep lam adi seng teenuh teewah tathike ngeh ih noisok tan. 
\p  
\v 12 Erah raangtaan ih, le raangtang bah uh, o mina emoong reeta thoidi tah angta adoleh o moongta erah suh taraang tang. Erah nang ebah, Rangte miksok di sen ih amiisak di seng mathan thun hali erah jatthuk suh raangtang.  
\v 13 Erah raangtaan ih seng rap eh seng rangdongli. 
\p Seng rangdong luulu lah angthang ih; Taitaas ah chosok anno heh tenroon thuktan ah suh seng rapne ih roonti.  
\v 14 Ngah sen suh khuupook lang tiit ah heh suh baat etang, sen ih ngah tarakrek thukri. Sen loong ah damdi saarookwet seng amiitiit ah roongwaanti, erah likhiikkhiik sen raangtaan ih seng rangdong tiit Taitaas suh baatti ah ih amiisak angkah ngeh ih noisok ha.  
\v 15 Erah raangtaan ih heh ih ehanhan eh minchan halan, heh ih kah renbaat tahan adi sen ih mamah kah ih bantho tan nyia kamocho tan heh ih samthun roh eha.  
\v 16 Sen loong asuh jirep ni tuumaang laalom rum haano ngah rapne ih roonlang! 
\c 8  
\s1 Kristaan lakkot 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1 \xt Rom 15:26\x* Joon awaan loong, Mesidonia chaas loong adi Rangte minchan ah mathan angta erah jatthuk suh liihi.  
\v 2 Neng loong ah phate joonnaam rumta doh rapne ih chamnaang rumta; enoothong neng loong tenroon ah erah than ehan angta, neng lakkot ah uh datniikniik eh kotsuh nook rumta, neng loong ah changthih taat angrum abah uh ah.  
\v 3 Ngah ih sen loong asuh jen baat ih rumha neng ih mathan jen koh ah erah than ih koh rumta, eno erah nang ih ehan botse korumta. Neng ten ih jam ano  
\v 4 Judia dowa Rangte mina loong ah seng ih nep roong sokboi ih ngeh ih chuut hu rum ano seng lasih jotahe.  
\v 5 Seng laalomti ah nang ih ju ehan ih re rumta! Jaakhothoon ah neng Teesu suh look rumta; erah lih adi, Rangte thung jun di neng teewah seng sak ni uh look haat eh rumtaha.  
\v 6 Erah jun ih seng loong ah Taitaas reeni chuut huuti, an phang mokah tu ah neng raangtaan ih heh minchan mootkaat ah maang thoonthoon ih mootjih ang ah ngeh ah.  
\v 7 Sen loong jiinni tiimjih jeela erah kapjap han adi sen loong ah rapne changteng: hanpi di angkoja oh, tiit baat di angkoja oh, adoleh mongtham di angkoja oh, erah damdi seng chosok hali nyia minchan ih hali adi nep ah.\f + \fr 8:7 \fq minchan ih hali; \ft mararah le ni liiha \fq seng minchan ah sen raangtaan.\f* Eno sen loong ah arah minchan mootkaat adoh uh larat lapatte toom ang an ih liihi. 
\p  
\v 8 Ngah ih sen hopnak suh nyia pansuh tali kang. Enoothong wahoh loong ah mih chosok suh mamah ih nookla, erah likhiik sen loong mongnook amiisak di mathan ah erah jat suh liihang.  
\v 9 Sen loong ah ih seng Teesu Jisu Kristo minchan ah jat ehan; heh changteng ang abah uh, sen raangtaan ih heh teewah changthih ih hoon thukta, tiimnge liidi heh changthet jun ih sen changteng toom ih hoon an ngeh ah. 
\p  
\v 10 Ngah ih thunhang manrang phang mokatan ah amadoh jentom mokah anbah ese ang ah. Sen loong ah mootkaat pakna ni luulu kapkhoh tah angtan, reeraang pakna suh uh ethun ih tan.  
\v 11 Emah ang abah, mootkaatjih ah thoon mootkaat ih an! Sen ih echaan ih thoon mootkaat suh thuntan ah mamah jen reeraang pakna an erah jun ih thoon mokah an eno amadi tiim reeraangjih ah erah mokah an.  
\v 12 Sen loong ah ekot esuh nook elan bah, sen suh jeela jun ih sen lakkot ah Rangte ih ethang ih ah, lajeeka bah tiimma thang ah.  
\v 13-14 Ngah ih sen loong ah naangcham thuk rum haano wahoh naangtong thuk suh taliikang; enoothong amadi sen suh saapoot je thoidi ba, ramtek khamle tongte loong ah chosok anbah ese ang ah ngeh ih baat rumhala. Eno juuba, sen loong ramtek khamle tong an doh nyia neng suh je adoh neng ih uh toom chosok han. Erah likhiik sen loongtang eluilui ang theng.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt Hpkt 16:18\x* Rangteele ni amah liiha, “O ih ehan lomhui ha erah suh ehan tah angka, eno o ih amasah lomhui ha he suh eneethoon tah angka.” 
\s1 Taitaas nyia heh lamjoonte 
\p  
\v 16 Rangte suh lakookmi liihi seng ih sen chosok suh thun hi ah likhiik Taitaas ih uh emamah ih thunha!  
\v 17 Heh suh baatti luulu lathang thang ih; heh thung ih uh sen chosok suh nyia sen reeni kaat thung angta.  
\v 18 Chaas rookwet ni ruurang ese tiit baat thoidi rapne ih choomjoh arah phoh ano wahoh loong nep heh damdi wakkaat thuk hali.  
\v 19 Erah tokkhoh di uh, minchan thoidi nyia Teesu rangka suh adoleh sen loong chosok ah noisok suh Chaaste loong ih heh seng damdoh roongkhoom theng ngeh ih danje nyia danjoh rumha. 
\p  
\v 20 Lakkot laknoi doh mih ih liilaang jih naktoom ang ah ngeh ih seng sokthun samthun ih reeli.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 8:21 \xt Tittk 3:4\x* Teesu miksok doh luulu lah angthang ih, mih miksok doh seng loong ah marah epun ah erah reejih. 
\p  
\v 22 Erah raangtaan ih Taitaas loong ah damdi seng loong no wakkaat thuk hali; seng ih saarookwet thaaksok ih di heh mih chosok suh ramram angte mina. Eno amadi sen loong asuh rapne laalom halan, sen chosok suh rapne ih ramla.  
\v 23 Taitaas ah langla, sen loong chosok suh nga damdi roong mootkaatte; phoh ano wahoh loong heh damdi o roongkhoom rumla langla, chaas loong mendi khoom rumla nyia Kristo men raksiitte.  
\v 24 Neng loong asuh sen mongnook ah noisok an, chaas loong ah erah suh emi tuumaang theng toom ang ah adoleh sen thoilam di seng loong khuupook li ah epun ekah ngeh ih toomjat rum ah. 
\c 9  
\s1 Changthih kristaan loong chosok 
\p  
\v 1 Judia ni Rangte mina loong kaat thuk halang ah chosok suh ngah ih sen suh le raangkot ju amiidi bah lapaklak jih angta.  
\v 2 Ngah ih jat ehang sen loong ah chosok suh eram elan, erah raangtaan ih Mesidonia mina loong suh sen suh khuupook lang ah noisok rumhang. Ngah ih liitang, “Akaia dowa hanpiite loong ah” “manrang dowa ih chosok esuh banban tong rumla.” Sen lakkot je thoidi neng loong ah ehanko ah lakkot laknoi thung.  
\v 3 Arah hanpiite loong ah amadi daapkaat eh halang, sen lakkot laknoi suh khuupookli ah thaangmuh jengkhaap naktoom ang ah. Enoothong, ngah ih liihang ah likhiik, sen loong ah lakkot laknoi suh banban bantong theng.  
\v 4 Enoothong, Mesidonia dowa mina loong ah nga damdoh mok roongra haadoh sen lakkot suh banban lamok angkan bah, seng tiimthan rakriijih ang ah—sen rakrek tiit ju lah angthang—sen su laalomli asuh ehan rakri theng ang ah.  
\v 5 Erah thoidi hanpiite loong ah nga ngani bankaat thuksuh samthuntang, neng ih sen lakkot kakham tan ah toom ban khookham rum ah suh ah. Eno juuba ngah thok hangdoh ban khookham choi ang ah, eno lakkot laknoi suh enook elan ngeh ih noisok ah, sen ekot etheng ngeh ih lah angthang eh ah. 
\p  
\v 6 Samthun etheng o mina ih hejih eneesah wen abah cham hemootsah ju ang ah; o ih ehan wen ah ehan ju choh ah.  
\v 7 Erah raangtaan ih, mamah ih kotsuh liitan, emamah ih kottheng, thetthun damdoh lakot theng nyia kot ejih angkatih ngeh ih lakottheng; tiimnge liidi Rangte ih o ih tenroon ih koha erate ah nook ha.  
\v 8 Adoleh mootse kaatse raangtaan ih Rangte ih sen ih jamhan ah nang ih ju ehan jen kohan, saarookwet nyia saapoot rookwet sen raangtaan ih jeeruh toom eh ah ngeh ah.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Rsb 112:9\x* Rangteele ni uh emah liiha, 
\q1 “Changthih noodek suh larat lapat ih koh adi; 
\q2 heh tenthet ah saarookwet raang ih tong ah. 
\m  
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt Isa 55:10\x* Eno Rangte, o ih chamwente suh raanjih kotte nyia phaksat esuh baanlo kotte warah ih larat lapat kot kano raanjih thoontang kohan, eno erah rapne ih seethuk ah.  
\v 11 Jaarookwet naktoom ratpat ah ngeh ih sen changteng angthuk han, tiimnge liidi sen ih kohali ah neng suh toom kohi thoidoh warep ih Rangte suh saarookwet lakookmi toomli rum ah.  
\v 12 Sen erah reeraang lan ah Rangte mina loong raangtaan luulu tah angka, enoothong Rangte suh ehanhan ih lakookmi li theng ih hoonla.  
\v 13 Eno erah pakna reeraang lan jun ih, nyia Kristo ruurangese tiit ah kap kanno adoleh amadi, neng suh kohan nyia wareprep suh chokoh han thoidoh warep ih Rangte rangka ah.  
\v 14 Eno Rangte ih hedakdak minchan noisok kohanno neng loong ah ih rapne ih thun damdoh rangsoom kohan.  
\v 15 Ranglakkot thaangmuh kot thoidoh loongtang ih Rangte suh lakookmi li ih! 
\c 10  
\s1 Rangte mootkaat raang ih Pool laatta 
\p  
\v 1 Pool, ngah ih, sen lasih jorum hala—sen damdi roongtong hang di mih ih toongtang nyia ese li halang, enoothong haloh ang angdi mithih li halang. Kristo minchan nyia tenthet ih  
\v 2 sen reenah wanghang doh mithih nakkah angthuk weehe; tiimnge liidi o ih mongrep tenthun nawa ih re rumla ngeh ih li hali erah damdi mithih likhiik ih reeli.  
\v 3 Amiisak di elang eh ah seng arah mongrep adi songtong li, enoothong mongrep tenthun ni tarookmuike.  
\v 4 Seng rookmuili lang apah ah arah mongrep dowa lang apah tah angka erabah Rangte chaan aphaan lang apah, erah lang apah rah ih echeh echaan loong ah thet haat hi. Tiitmoong jengkhaap di daanmui li loong ah seng ih thet haat ehi;  
\v 5 Rangte mongtham ngathong ni khuupookli adi seng lamtang hali ah thet haat ehi; warep tenthun ah seng lakhui ni angthuk eno Kristo tiit ah kap thuk hi.  
\v 6 Sen loong ah hejeng chaatchaat ngeh ih noisok an, jeng laboichaatte loong ah cham thuk suh seng loong ah ban tongli. 
\p  
\v 7 Tiim ang abah uh sen ih rangkhoh toloh ni sok han. O ih bah uh senteewah Kristo raangtaan ngeh ih thun tam ehan? Ese, neng teewah suh emah toom we samthun rum ah, tiimnge liidi neng ih samthunha likhiik seng uh emamah Kristo mina ju.  
\v 8 Teesu ih chaan aphaan kohali asuh khuupook ih bah uh nga tarakri kang—erah chaan aphaan ah sen toonjoot theng, sen dat hoom theng tah angka.  
\v 9 Nga ih le korum haano sen cho thuk suh taliikang.  
\v 10 Mararah ih liiha “Pool le ah echeh echaan, enoothong heteewah ah hephuuphu seng damdoh ang haano, heh larook lata ih hoonla, eno heh jengkhaap ah tiimju tah angka!”  
\v 11 Erah likhiik mina ih jat etheng seng sen reeni lah angke di le ni tiimjih raang kohi nyia sen damdi ang edi tiimjih reeli ah phoosiit. 
\p  
\v 12 Elang eh ah o ih ngah elong thunha damdi seng teeteewa tanaan toobaatke. Neng loong ah tiimthan ngakthakla! Erah loong ah ebah neng thun jun ih neng teeteewah thaak samthunha nyia neng teeteewah thaak dande ha!  
\v 13 Enoothong, seng loong ah kaaliin takhuupookke; Rangte ih mathan mootkaat thuk hali erah mongmong adoh ang ah, eno arah sen damdi moli rah uh erah mongmong adi moli.  
\v 14 Eno seng ih Kristo Ruurang Ese tiit baatkaat tahe adoh, sen ih mathan samjat an erah than ba baatti, erah nang eh ehan jiitbaat muh.  
\v 15 Erah thoidi seng suh Rangte ih mathan reetheng thiinkoh hali wahoh loong ah erah nang ih ehan mokala asuh takhuupookke. Erah nang ebah, saarookwet Rangte ih mathan mootkaat theng thiinkoh hali, sen jaachi nah sen loong ah ehanhan ih jen mootkaat suh hanpi han asuh ba laalomli.  
\v 16 Eno juuba seng lakngah nah deek hoh nah Ruurang Ese tiit jen jiit baatkaat ih, eno wahoh phek ni jen mootkaat choi asuh takhuupookke. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Jer 9:24\x* Enoothong Rangteele ni liiha, “O bah uh khuupook esuh li abah Teesu ih tiimjih mokala erah suh khuupook theng.”  
\v 18 Tiimnge liidi Teesu ih seng suh ese ngeh ih thun ano kap hali adi ba seng loong ah epun eli, eno seng teeteewah ih maama teewah suh ese thunhi adi tah angka. 
\c 11  
\s1 Pool nyia tiitmoong baatte kaamwah loong 
\p  
\v 1 Ngah mok ngakthak ang bah nyia baangthaang angbah sen ih enaan ehe ngeh ih laalom lang. Emah ju angwe an!  
\v 2 Rangte sen suh lungwaang hala likhiik, ngah uh sen loong suh lungwaang halang; sen loong ah jaalasah toongtang likhiik marah wasiit luulu damdoh kuhoon thuk suh kakhat rumhala, erah langla Kristo heteewah.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 11:3 \xt Rangph 3:1-5,13\x* Ngah choolang abah senthung sentak ah chikrok anno Kristo lih seklilih ih phanhan nyia saachamcham ih mokalan ah ma thiinhaat jan oh— erah likhiik pu ih heh mongtham ethih nawa ih Ip mokwaanta.  
\v 4 Sen loong ah ih o wangkoha bah uh seng ih baattaan hi Jisu, tiit lah angthang ih, Jisu wahoh tiit baattaan kohan bah uh boichaat roroh ehan nyi enaan ehan; adoleh seng jiinnawa chaat han Chiiala nyia ruurangese tiit likhiik lah angthang eh jihoh chiiala nyia ruurangese tiit ah mok kap han! 
\p  
\v 5 Ngah ih thun angdi sen loong ah ih “kaamwah loong” asuh hoondak eh liihan ah nang ih ngah ehin nyia lajat tah angkang.  
\v 6 Ngah lanang miijeng kangbah uh, mongtham lajat tah angkang, erah tiit ah sen loong asuh saapoot rookwet nyia jirep thoidi saasa ih baat hi. 
\p  
\v 7 Rangte Ruurang Ese tiit nyootsoot rum taha thaang ngah tiim uh tasuh rum taha, sen loong ah hoondak mina toom ang an ngeh ih nga teewah subah elong tali tang. Eno nga moongre tam etang?  
\v 8 Sen loong damdi mokah tahang adi nga subah ehoh chaas loong ah ih kot kotahang, weeli ang bah, erah sen loong chosok suh neng loong ah taangnawa ngeekot rum kotaha.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 11:9 \xt Phl 4:15-18\x* Eno sen damdi ang tahang tokdi uh ngun laaki angbah uh sen tabansok rum taha; tiim laaki ang bah uh Mesidonia nawa wangte kristaan loong ah ih chokot rum kotahang. Erah raangtaan ih ehakdi angkoja oh, adoleh liwang nah angkoja oh: nga raangtaan ih sen sootboot theng tah angka!  
\v 10 Kristo amiisak tiit ah nga taangni je tungkaangdi, ngah ih kakham hang Akaia nah manah ang ang bah uh ngah khuupook lang ah ehotthiinjih tah angka.  
\v 11 Erah jenglang ah sen lanook rumra no tam jenglang? Rangte ih jat eha ngah ih sen enook ih rum hala ngeh ah. 
\p  
\v 12 “Kaamwah” wahoh loong ah ih tiim thoilam ni ang abah uh neng mokala ah likhiik seng uh emamah ju mokali nge ih khuupook rumla eno neng lakhuupook thuk suh amadi reelang ah likhiik ju re ang.  
\v 13 Erah miwah loong ah amiisak kaamwah tah angka—erah loong abah lalangka kaamwah, neng mootkaat tiit ehu baatrum ano neng teewah rangkhotoloh ni amiisak Kristo kaamwah ngeh ih noisok rumha.  
\v 14 Ese, erah suh tapaatja ke! Soitaan ih uh heteewah ah rangkhotoloh ni weephaak rangsah likhiik ih noisok ha.  
\v 15 Erah raangtaan ih heh laksuh loong ah ih neng teeteewah kateng laksuh likhiik ih rangkhotoloh ni noisok ha ah tarakka. Saathoon doh neng tiim chotheng ah erarah ju chorum ah. 
\s1 Kaamwah ang thoidi Pool chamnaangta 
\p  
\v 16 Arah we dopjeng lang: O ih bah uh nakmok thunhe ngah thungko ngeh ah. Enoothong emah mokthun anbah, thungko jengla ngeh ih taan boichaat ih an, tiimnge liidi nga erah suh amasah taan jen khuupook suh ah.  
\v 17 Amadi arah jenglang ah Teesu ih lajeng thuk rang ah uh mok jeng e ang; arah jo khuupook jenglang ah thungko jengjeng ju elang.  
\v 18 Enoothong wareprep ah mina ang kangtih ngeh ih khuupookla, ah likhiik ngah uh emamah taalek ang langnih.  
\v 19 Sen teeteewah erah than ejat ang anno, o ih mokwaan kohan erah loong jeng ah tenroon woksoon eh boichaat roh roh ih han nyia enaan ehan.  
\v 20 O ih baat kohan bah uh nyia joonnaan kohan bah uh, phoong tung han bah uh adoleh damnak ehan bah uh nyia sen the ni baangbuhan bah uh boichaat roh roh nyia naan roh ehan.  
\v 21 Erah loong ah reeraang suh echo eti ngeh ih thang suh rakrek elang! 
\p Enoothong tiim thoilam di ang abah uh o jen khuupook ah—ngah thungko likhiik ih jengkong lang—ngah uh emamah jen khuupook ang.  
\v 22 Neng loong ah Hebru tam ah? Ngah uh emah ju. Neng loong ah Ijirelte tam ah? Ngah uh emah ju. Neng loong ah Abraham sutoom tam ah? Ngah uh emah ju.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 11:23 \xt Esm 16:23\x* Neng loong ah Kristo laksuh tam ah? Ngah emok epaang likhiik jengkong lang—enoothong ngah neng nang ebah laksuh ang ang bah uh eseethoon! Echeh echaan loong ah ngah mokah lang, phaatak ni hedop hedop sak halang, ruh nawa ih ngah ehan buh halang, eno tiimsaasa di tek thanthan ih chamlang.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 11:24 \xt Hodb 25:3\x* Dop bangnga di Jehudi loong ah ih rookjom ja akhuh ruh ih burum tahang;  
\v 25 \x - \xo 11:25 \xt Esm 16:22; 14:19\x* Room hate ih ruh nawa ih dopjom burum tahang; eno jaasiit ah jong ih patrum tahang. Juukaari khoodatta adi takjom chamlang, eno jaasiit adi hephe pheesiit hesa saasiit ju khoni angtang.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 11:26 \xt Esm 9:23; \xt Esm 14:5\x* Erah tumkhoom tang adi juujeng naamnak di nyi ehuh epaang damdi hedop hedop tungthang tang, nga mina loong nyia Ranglajatte loong damdi choophaan phaan ih angtang; samnuthung ni uh echo etheng angta, phima woma ni echo etheng angta, juusih ni echo etheng angta, eno lalangka joon awaan loong ra uh echo theng angta.  
\v 27 Jupmuh saatmuh mootkaat theng angta; tiim saasa di jupmuh saatmuh mokatang; ramtek khamle damdi mokatang; tiim saasa di phak asat larooklui, naangjam theng laje nyia nyuh akhat larooklui ih angtang.  
\v 28 Eno jihoh tiit ju labaat, chaas loong raangtaan ih ngah ehan sootboot tang.  
\v 29 O ang abah uh larook lata angta adi ngah uh larook lata roong hoontang, mabah o mina rangdajih re adi, ngah sootsaam etang. 
\p  
\v 30 Ngah khuupookjih jaatjaat ang abah, larook lata angtang noisok ha asuh ba jen khuupook ang.  
\v 31 Rangte nyia Teesu Jisu Wah—men juuba saarookwet raangtaan ih romseetam toom ang ah—heh ih jat eha ngah ih tiit hu tabaatkang ngeh ah.  
\v 32 \x - \xo 11:32 \xt Esm 9:23-25\x* Ngah Damaskas ni angtang adoh, kobono ih nga khak thuk suh samnuthung pa kaawaan ni bante loong tongthuk rumta, erah tokdi Aritas ah Luuwang angta.  
\v 33 Enoothong koiraangpo lam ih hong ni datthiin rumhang no bante loong lak nawa puitang. 
\c 12  
\s1 Pool mot amang tiitwu 
\p  
\v 1 Nga khuupook ah laseeka bah uh, ngah khuupook roh ete anglang. Enoothong ngah ih mot amang nyia Teesu ih tiitwu halang tiit ah baat ang.  
\v 2 Asih paangbaji ngani rangmong echoong thoon ni kristaan mina wasiit siitwanta warah ngah ih jat ehang (Enoothong erah ngah ih tajatkang amiidi tam ang kotaaja adoleh mot amang sok kotaaja—Rangte ih luulu ba jat ah.)  
\v 3-4 Ngah we dopjeng lang, arah mih ah Wojum ni siitwanta (Erah uh, amiimi tam ang kotaaja tam aleh mot amang angko taaja—Rangte ih luulu ba jat ah), eno erah di heh ih jengkhaap lam ih lami dongbaat theng nyia mina tuikhoop ni lami jeng theng japchaatta.  
\v 5 Erah raangtaan ih nga teewah suh takhuupook kang —enoothong arah mina asuh khuupook lang, nga teewah larook lata asuh ba khuupook lang.  
\v 6 Ngah khuupook e ang bah uh, engak tah e kang, mamah liidi ngah ih ami tiit ah lekbaat angdoh ah. Enoothong ngah takhuupook kang, tiimnge liidi sen ih ngah jiin nawa tiimjih tup tan nyia chaat tan ah, erah o suh ang abah uh nga tiit ah ehan ih rangbaat thuk suh ngah tanookkang. 
\p  
\v 7 Enoothong epaatjaajih jirep ah japtup thoidoh naktoom khuupook ah li ano, nga hansi ni sattitih ih chamthuk tahang, erah langla nga siiwi chamnaang thuk suh nyia thungjoong thuk suh Soitaan kaamwah ih satthuk ah likhiik ih ang thukta eno takhuupook thuk tahang.  
\v 8 Erah khoisat ah deesiit raangtaan ih Teesu suh nga rangsoom ni jaajom baattang.  
\v 9 Enoothong heh ih ngaakbaat tahang: “An raangtaan ih nga minchan ah laaleh ang ah, tiimnge liidi larook lata ang udi nga chaanphaan ah rakla.” Erah thoidi, nga larook lata ang angdi, nga pangte Kristo chaanphaan asuh tenroon anglang.  
\v 10 Kristo thoilam di, larook lata, thaangju kaanse, echam enaang, siiwii nyia echeh echaan loong ah roongje roh e hala. Tiimnge liidi ngah larook lata ang angdi, tathat eh hoon lang. 
\s1 Pool ih Korinte thuntak tiit 
\p  
\v 11 Ngah thungko likhiik ih reeraang lang—enoothong erah sen ih reeraang thuk hali. Nga tiit roong seebaatte ah sen angjih angtan. Tiimnge liidi lidoh tiim lajo ang kangbah uh, sen loong “kaamwah” wahoh loong nang ih ngah ehin tah angkang.  
\v 12 Sen jaachi ni paatjaajih nyia epaattek etheng jirep ah enaan lam ih re kangno ngah kaamwah ngeh ih noisok halan.  
\v 13 Chaas wahote nang ih ethih mamah miili he, ngun akom di ba sen suh talaalom tahang? Erah raangtaan ih lalangka mok reetang ah biin anaan hoon weehe. 
\p  
\v 14 Arah ih jaajom ang ah ngah sen reeni dongkhoom suh ban khookham hang—enoothong sen taangnawa tiim uh tasuh rumra. Ngah ih ngun tajam kang, sen loong ba jam rumhala. Tiimnge liidi, hesuh hehsah loong ih henuh hewah loong suh tajam koka, henuh hewah ih ba jamkoh ah  
\v 15 Sen loong chosok raangtaan ih ngaapuh ngaasak dowa ih nga jiinni tiim jeela, erah loong kot suh nga tenroon lang. Nga ih ehan eh nook rum kohaano sen ih tatam nookri? 
\p  
\v 16 Erah suh nook anbah, nga raangtaan ih sen sootboot theng tah angta. Enoothong mararah ih mokli an, ngah maakthih maklang nyia sen mokwaan suh tiit hu baatrum hala ngeh ah.  
\v 17 Mamah ma ang ah? Ngah ih kongphaak kotte daapkaat tahang loong ah jun ih sen loong ah tam put thuk rum taha?  
\v 18 Sen reeni kaat thuk suh Taitaas lasih jotang, eno heh damdi wahoh hanpiite nep wakra thuk tahang. Sen ih Taitaas ih nep eput eh tahe tam liihan? Sek wanyiinyi jisiit mootkaat raang ih phoosiitsiit tanih reeti tih? 
\p  
\v 19 Sen loong ih mokthun an madoh dowa ih seng ih seng tiit asuh ese ih baat hi ngeh ah. Emah tah angka! Joon awaan loong Rangte ngathong ni, tiim re ih bah uh sen chosok suh nyia Kristo ih jeng thuk he ah likhiik ih ba jengli.  
\v 20 Ngah erah raacho lang, sen reenah raahang adoh nga thung jun doh lah ang, adoleh sen thung jun doh uh lah ang ma mok japtup jang oh ngeh ah. Ngah choolang ah langla, rookmui jengmui adoleh khaada mui, tenkhat nyia lup aleek, kaanju nyia mokwaan mui, joobaat waanbaat mui, miksuh siikhaam mui, adoleh lalang lajang khuupook arah ma japtup jang oh ngeh ah.  
\v 21 Nga erah raacho lang, alih adoh dong raahang adoh sen ngathong nah Rangte ih kaanju ete ang halang, eno ehakdi data nyia ehuh eleek, roomjup roomtong loong rangdah lah sekthun loong ah raangtaan ih ngah ehu ete—erah langla neng loong ramka nyia roomjup roomtong thoidoh ang ah. 
\c 13  
\s1 Choophaan nyia Jengseera thoonjeng 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 13:1 \xt Hodb 17:6\x*Sen loong reeni arah dong ra halang ah ih takjom ang ah. “Tiimjaat thikhah ih doh uh wanyi adoleh ehan ih haaki ko ano ba jen paat ah—rangteele ni liiha jun ih ah.  
\v 2 Ehakdi o datan, nyia wahoh loong asuh baat rumhala; arah tiit ah sen reeni dopnyi dong ra tahang adoh baatchoi, enoothong sen loong reenawa haloh ni ang ang bah uh arah we baat rumhala: Arah lih adoh raahang adoh hoocham chotheng nawa o uh tapuikan.  
\v 3 Kristo ah nga jun ih waan hala eno sen ih jamhan ah jaatrep erah doh dongjat an. Heh sen damdi tiimdi bah uh larook lata tah angka; erah nang ebah, sen loong dung ni chaan aphaan ba noisok halan.  
\v 4 Rapne ih naangti adi heh bangphak ni tekrapbotta bah uh, Rangte chaan aphaan nawa ih heh ething tongla. He damdi roop eno seng loong uh enaang eli, enoothong sen damdi joonte sano pak ih no heh roidong adi Rangte chaan aphaan ni roongroop eli. 
\p  
\v 5 Maama teenuh teewah thaaksok nyia thaak dande ih an, sen loong ah tuumaang lam ih tam songtong lan. Amiisak di sen ih jat ehan Jisu Kristo ah sen damdi eje ngeh ah—sen loong ah jirep di maangthoon thikhah kandoh thaak sok eh an.  
\v 6 Sen loong suh ngah tuumaang elang, seng ih jirep ah ejen eh ih.  
\v 7 Sen lathetre suh nyia lamoongtaang suh seng ih rangsoom hi—erah langla seng ih jirep ah jenta ehi ngeh ih tah angka, enoothong seng loong ah lajenke ah likhiik ang ih bah uh, sen loong ah ih marah epun ah erah toom mokah an ngeh ih re li.  
\v 8 Tiimnge liidi amiisak tiit ngathong nah seng tiim uh tami reeraang ke, enoothong amiisak raangtaan ih reeraang pakna theng.  
\v 9 Seng loong ah larook lata di eroon eli enoothong sen loong ah tathat anglan. Erah raangtaan ih erah nang ih ju eseethoon toom ang an ngeh ih rangsoom kohi.  
\v 10 Erah raangtaan ih sen loong reeni lah ang kangbah uh arah le ah raangkoh rumhala; erah langla Teesu ih kohalang chaan aphaan ah sen loong reenah dongkhoom hang adoh sen ih laan thichoh roh lamaak suh—erah chaan aphaan kohalang ah sen thet hoom suh tah angka sen loong rongthu raangtaan ih kohalang. 
\p  
\v 11 Joon awaan loong amadi sen loong damdi raajeng rumhala! Eseethoon raangtaan sen loong ah mokah an; sen loong asuh jengse jeng koh rumhala ah boichaat eh an; loongtang wasiit wasiit damdoh ese angtheng; semroongroong ih songtong an. 
\p  
\v 12 Semroongroong songtong anno wasiit ih wasiit suh jengseera an. 
\p Rangte mina loongtang ih sen loong asuh jengseera halan. 
\p  
\v 13 Teesu Jisu Kristo minchan, Rangte mongnook, nyia Esa Chiiala roongtong hala ah sen damdoh toom angha .